        "text": "Let me tell you about the Hargrove kitchen.\n\nIn 2024, the Hargroves installed a premium smart refrigerator. It learned their habits within a week. It knew when Marcus wanted orange juice (6:47 AM, weekdays only) and when Diane switched from whole milk to oat (the third week of...",
